R Chunk

# R chunk
# 裏面可以寫R語法，跟平常一樣
# 要注意，每次輸出html，都會整個.rmd重跑，所以library那些都要寫在chunk裏面
#default: message=TRUE
library(dplyr)
## 
## Attaching package: 'dplyr'
## The following objects are masked from 'package:stats':
## 
##     filter, lag
## The following objects are masked from 'package:base':
## 
##     intersect, setdiff, setequal, union
#### 無設定
r paste('aaa')
## [1] "aaa"

echo=F

## [1] "aaa"
paste('aaa')
plot(iris$Sepal.Length,iris$Sepal.Width)

如果想output顯示在console,可以按上方的齒輪調整

如果你想要每個chunk都隱藏message及warning,不需逐個設定,設定多數放在最開始執行

knitr::opts_chunk$set(
    message = FALSE,
    warning = FALSE
)
